{"title":"Deodorant","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"deodorant-cosmebio-without-aluminum-salts-without-alcohol-without-parabens-50ml","title":"Deodorant Cosmébio Without Aluminum Salts Without Alcohol Without Parabens 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe natural and certified organic “Avoir 20 Ans” alcohol-free roll-on deodorant has been tested effective for 24 hours. It is also free of aluminum salts and parabens. The aloe vera contained in the treatment makes it very moisturizing, it is ideal after hair removal to avoid redness. Its antibacterial active ingredients prevent appearance of post-depilatory pimples. Its small ball allows it to be applied precisely and it does not stain clothes. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt is suitable for all skin types. Its creamy texture and very light 100% natural orange blossom fragrance will delight you every day.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/b\u003eThe “Avoir 20 Ans” deodorant is used in the morning and\/or evening after a shower on clean, dry skin, applying gently under the armpits. Repeat the application during the day when you feel the need.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eAqua, hordeum vulgare stem water*, caprylic\/capric triglycerides, triethyl citrate, cetearyl alcohol, glyceryl stearate, glycerin, stearic acid, prunus persica juice, aloe vera barbadensis powder*, tocopherol, helianthus annuus seed oil, salvia officinalis (sage) oil , sodium caproyl\/lauroyl lactyl lactate, sodium lauroyl glutamate, xanthan gum, citric acid, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate, benzyl alcohol, dehydroacetic acid, fragrance, linalool, limonene, geraniol, citral.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* Ingredient from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e** Processed from ingredients from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade in France.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e99.5% natural ingredients, 12.9% from organic farming and mainly from fair trade\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAll raw materials processed in France\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeodorant made in France (Alsace)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNo controversial ingredients, 100% good for your skin and the enivironment\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTotal absence of palm oil and its derivatives\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePackaging: 100% recycled and recyclable bottle made in Europe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"FUN!ETHIC","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49112020844871,"sku":null,"price":6.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/deodorant-cosmebio-without-aluminum-salts-without-alcohol-without-parabens-50ml-431679.png?v=1739897342"},{"product_id":"madara-herbal-deodorant-50ml","title":"MÁDARA Herbal Deodorant 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis quick-drying deodorant with Northern sage and natural minerals reduces odour and provides all-day freshness. Quickly-absorbing formula leaves no stains on the clothes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply to clean underarms. Use daily.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Glycerin, Potassium Alum, Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Water, Alcohol, Chondrus Crispus (Irish moss) powder, Aroma, Calendula Officinalis (Calendula) Flower Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Camomile) Flower Extract, Mentha Piperita (Peppermint) Leaf Extract, Salvia Officinalis (Salvia) Leaf Extract, Benzyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene, Linalool, Geraniol, Citronellol, Citral\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916399677767,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-herbal-deodorant-50ml-496779.jpg?v=1739897151"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-deodorant-cream-neutral-50ml","title":"Blokzeep Deodorant Cream - Neutral 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the Neutral deodorant cream is suitable for everyone. This is a deodorant without perfume or essential oils. The active ingredients in our natural deodorant are corn starch and baking soda. These fabrics absorb moisture naturally and are therefore ideal against perspiration. In addition, it is good for the care and strengthening of your skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis natural deodorant cream is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Deodorant cream is packaged in an aluminum can, which has the highest recycling rate (95%) of all possible packaging. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eStickers on packages are made from PaperWise – agricultural waste. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Deodorant cream contains 100% natural ingredients that are good for you and our planet. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Deodorant cream is handmade and completely Vegan. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Deodorant cream is plastic-free and palm oil-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEvery Block Soap deodorant is perfume-free and aluminum-free. The deodorant cream contains only natural ingredients, such as baking soda. By using baking soda in deodorants, your skin flora is not disturbed and you prevent your pores from becoming clogged. A can of natural deodorant cream lasts about three months and is ideal for at home and on the go. Due to the handy packaging, the natural deodorant cream is also allowed on the plane and at festivals.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply on armpits as needed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eZea Mays Starch, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Sodium Bicarbonate, Cocos Nucifera Oil, CI 77947\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50965176549703,"sku":null,"price":9.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-deodorant-cream-neutral-50ml-486136.jpg?v=1739897190"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-deodorant-cream-tea-tree-50ml","title":"Blokzeep Deodorant cream - Tea tree 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural deodorant cream Tea Tree is a miracle remedy with versatile properties. In this way, Tea Tree prevents fatty acids from being converted into unpleasant odors, which makes it very suitable as an ingredient in our natural deodorant. In addition, Tea Tree has a disinfectant effect, works against skin conditions and cares for your skin. Furthermore, the active ingredients in the natural deodorant are corn starch and baking soda. These fabrics absorb moisture naturally and are therefore ideal against perspiration.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis natural deodorant cream is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Deodorant cream is packaged in an aluminum can, which has the highest recycling rate (95%) of all possible packaging. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eStickers on packages are made from PaperWise – agricultural waste. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Deodorant cream contains 100% natural ingredients that are good for you and our planet. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Deodorant cream is handmade and completely Vegan, it \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eis plastic-free and palm oil-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEvery Block Soap deodorant is perfume-free and aluminum-free. The deodorant cream contains only natural ingredients, such as baking soda. By using baking soda in deodorants, your skin flora is not disturbed and you prevent your pores from becoming clogged. A can of natural deodorant cream lasts about three months and is ideal for at home and on the go. Due to the handy packaging, the natural deodorant cream is also allowed on the plane and at festivals.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply on armpits as needed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eZea Mays Starch, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Sodium Bicarbonate, Cocos Nucifera Oil, CI 77947, Melaleuca Alternifo lia Leaf Oil , Limonene\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50965208203591,"sku":null,"price":9.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-deodorant-cream-tea-tree-50ml-537151.jpg?v=1739897177"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-deodorant-cream-grapefruit-50ml","title":"Blokzeep Deodorant cream - Grapefruit 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn addition to the refreshing scent, Grapefruit has antibacterial and antiseptic effects and is therefore very suitable for regulating sweat. In addition, Grapefruit oil has astringent and detoxifying properties and is good for firming the skin. The combination of the wonderful scent of Grapefruit and its positive properties makes Grapefruit very suitable for our natural cream deodorant. Furthermore, the active ingredients in our natural deodorant are corn starch and baking soda. These fabrics absorb moisture naturally and are therefore ideal against perspiration. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis natural deodorant cream is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Deodorant cream is packaged in an aluminum can, which has the highest recycling rate (95%) of all possible packaging. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eStickers on packages are made from PaperWise – agricultural waste. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Deodorant cream contains 100% natural ingredients that are good for you and our planet. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Deodorant cream is handmade and completely Vegan, it \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eis plastic-free and palm oil-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEvery Block Soap deodorant is perfume-free and aluminum-free. The deodorant cream contains only natural ingredients, such as baking soda. By using baking soda in deodorants, your skin flora is not disturbed and you prevent your pores from becoming clogged. A can of natural deodorant cream lasts about three months and is ideal for at home and on the go. Due to the handy packaging, the natural deodorant cream is also allowed on the plane and at festivals.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply on armpits as needed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eZea Mays Starch, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Sodium Bicarbonate, Cocos Nucifera Oil, CI 77947, Citrus Paradisi Peel Oil, Limonene, Linalool, Citral\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50965221867847,"sku":null,"price":9.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-deodorant-cream-grapefruit-50ml-550789.jpg?v=1739897182"},{"product_id":"luuv-deodorant-citrus-bliss-50ml","title":"LUUV Deodorant Citrus Bliss 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eCitrus natural deodorant with deodorizing agents that ensure you feel fresh, cheerful, and energized all day long. With 24-hour proven protection against unpleasant odors.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe deodorant allows the skin to breathe freely and does not interfere with its natural functions or clog pores. LUUV's secret weapons are sweat-absorbing rice starch and antibacterial sage extract. Additionally, the deodorant contains moisturizing and soothing aloe vera, gently nurturing underarm skin. The harmonious blend of citrus essential oils creates a delightful scent bouquet.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDries quickly and leaves no stains on clothes. And best of all, the deodorant is free from aluminum, alcohol, and baking soda, and is 100% vegan!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24h protection\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnergizing citrus scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-irritating\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-comedogenic\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizes and soothes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePreserves skin’s natural function\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree from soda, alcohol, and aluminum\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to clean underarms. Use daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Zinc Ricinoleate, Tetrasodium Glutamate Diacetate,Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Propanediol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Triethyl Citrate, Polyglyceryl-3-Caprylate, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract, Citric acid, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Oil (Orange oil), Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Xanthan Gum, Parfum, Limonene, Linalool, Citral, Benzyl Salicylate, Hydroxycitronellal, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138062283079,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deodorant-citrus-bliss-50ml-1045610.png?v=1756222797"},{"product_id":"luuv-deodorant-soothing-comfort-50ml","title":"LUUV Deodorant Soothing Comfort 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLUUV Soothing deodorant with natural deodorizing agents prevents the formation of body odor and absorbs excess sweat. With 24 hours of proven protection, you can feel fresh and energized all day long!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDeodorant does not disrupt the skin’s natural functioning and does not clog pores. Rice starch in the deodorant absorbs sweat, while sage extract has antibacterial properties. Additionally, it contains moisturizing aloe vera, which nourishes and soothes the skin under the arms – an ideal choice for sensitive skin! The deodorant dries quickly and does not leave stains on clothes. The organic and enchanting floral scent refreshes both body and mind.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSoothing deodorant is free from aluminum, alcohol, and baking soda, and is 100% vegan!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24h protection\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePleasent mild floral scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-irritating\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-comedogenic\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizes and soothes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePreserves skin’s natural function\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree from soda, alcohol and aluminum\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to clean underarms. Use daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Zinc Ricinoleate, Tetrasodium Glutamate Diacetate, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Propanediol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Triethyl Citrate,Polyglyceryl-3-Caprylate, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract, Citric acid, Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) oil, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Xanthan Gum, Parfum, Geraniol, Linalool, Limonene, Citral\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138114416967,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deodorant-soothing-comfort-50ml-7238915.png?v=1756222794"},{"product_id":"luuv-deodorant-lemongrass-green-50ml","title":"LUUV Deodorant Lemongrass Green 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLUUV Unisex deodorant with natural deodorizing agents prevents the formation of body odor and keeps you fresh and dry all day long!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe unisex deodorant allows the skin to function naturally and does not clog pores. Rice starch in the deodorant absorbs sweat, sage extract combats odor-causing bacteria, and aloe moisturizes and soothes delicate underarm skin. The deodorant dries quickly and does not leave stains on clothes. The fresh blend of essential oils is suitable for both men and women.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Unisex deodorant is certified with the globally recognized ECOCERT\/COSMOS certification, so you can be sure you’re using a product that’s not only good for you but also for our planet. Additionally, it is aluminum-free, alcohol-free, and soda-free, and 100% vegan!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24h protection \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh scent that is suitable for both men and women \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-irritating \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-comedogenic\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizes and soothes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePreserves skin’s natural function\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree from soda, alcohol, and aluminum\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to clean underarms. Use daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Zinc Ricinoleate, Tetrasodium Glutamate Diacetate, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Propanediol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Triethyl Citrate, Polyglyceryl-3-Caprylate, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract, Citric acid, Citrus Limon Peel (Lemon) Oil, Cymbopogon Flexuosus (Lemongrass) Oil, Citrus Aurantium Bergamia Fruit (Bergamot) Oil, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Xanthan Gum, Limonene, Citral, Linalool, Geraniol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138263904583,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deodorant-lemongrass-green-50ml-1178078.png?v=1756222794"},{"product_id":"luuv-deodorant-fresh-breeze-50ml","title":"LUUV Deodorant Fresh Breeze 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLUUV Fresh deodorant with natural deodorizing agents prevents the formation of body odor and keeps you fresh and dry all day long!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDeodorant allows the skin to breathe freely, does not disrupt the skin’s natural functioning, and does not clog pores. Rice starch in the deodorant absorbs sweat, while antibacterial sage extract combats odor-causing bacteria. Moisturizing and soothing aloe vera nourishes delicate underarm skin. The deodorant dries quickly and leaves no stains on your favorite clothes. The blend of green tea and lemon essential oils refreshes and invigorates both body and mind.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOur deodorant is free from aluminum, alcohol, and baking soda, and is 100% vegan!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24h protection\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh “green” scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-irritating\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-comedogenic\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizes and soothes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePreserves skin’s natural function\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree from soda, alcohol, and aluminum\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to clean underarms. Use daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Dunaliella Salina Extract, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Citrus Nobilis (Mandarin) Peel Oil, Citrus Aurantium (Orange) Peel Oil, Xanthan Gum, Triethyl Citrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Mica, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Raphanus Sativus (Radish) Root Extract, Citric Acid, Maltodextrin, Parfum, Citral, Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138317152583,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deodorant-fresh-breeze-50ml-6627868.png?v=1756222791"},{"product_id":"hoia-natural-deodorant-no-worries","title":"HOIA Natural Deodorant No Worries 40ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe updated natural deodorant NO WORRIES has a mild and fresh scent, glides smoothly on the skin, does not create a thick layer, and thanks to innovative new ingredients, effectively helps reduce both sweating and body odor.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHOIA deodorant NO WORRIES is 100% natural. It contains no aluminum, synthetic dyes, or fragrances and is free from parabens. No Worries deodorant helps you feel fresh all day long.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Gently push the product up a few millimeters from the bottom with your finger and apply a suitable amount under the armpits. Use several times a day if necessary. Store below 25°C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, *Cocos Nucifera oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Kaolin, *Maranta Arundinacea Root Extract, Triethyl Citrate, Zinc Ricinolate, Calamine\/ Triethoxyocaprylylsilane, *Abies Sibirica Needle oil, Cedrus Atlantica Bark oil, *Lavandula Angustifolia Herb oil, *Rosimarinus Officinalis Leaf oil, *Mentha Piperita Leaf oil, Citrus Limon Peel oil, Natural Aroma, **Limonene,**Linalool. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e **Natural component of essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52247209574727,"sku":null,"price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-natural-deodorant-no-worries-40ml-3892390.png?v=1756718908"},{"product_id":"hoia-natural-deodorant-with-saaremaa-herbs-50ml","title":"HOIA Natural Deodorant With Saaremaa Herbs 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe updated formula of the creamy deodorant with Saaremaa herbs contains clay and arrowroot powder to absorb moisture, along with natural active ingredients that effectively prevent the formation of unpleasant body odor.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe deodorant includes:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCoconut oil with antibacterial properties\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCocoa butter and beeswax to nourish, protect, and moisturize the skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEssential oils to inhibit bacterial growth and keep you feeling fresh\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHOIA cream deodorant is 100% natural, free from aluminum, synthetic colors, and fragrances, and is paraben-free. Our brand new cream deodorant allows you to feel fresh throughout the day.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply a small amount of cream deodorant to your armpits using your fingertips and gently massage it into the skin. Store the deodorant away from direct sunlight and s\u003c\/span\u003etore below 25°C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eMaranta Arundinacea Root powder, *Cocos Nucifera oil, *Theobroma Cacao seed butter, Kaolin, *Cera Alba, Sodium Bicarbonate, Triethyl Citrate, Zinc Ricinoleate, Tocopherol, *Salvia Officinalis extract, *Hyssopus Ocinalis Decumbens extract, *Lavendula Angustifolia Leaf oil, **Linalool, **Limonene.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e** Natural Component of essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52247217602887,"sku":null,"price":17.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-natural-deodorant-with-saaremaa-herbs-50ml-2089297.jpg?v=1756718913"},{"product_id":"nurme-mild-baby-shampoo-body-wash-200ml-copy","title":"NURME Natural Deodorant Lavender and Sage 80g","description":"\u003cdiv\u003eThe essential oils contained in deodorants have odor-neutralizing properties and, in addition, the baking soda in deodorants prevents the spread of odorous bacteria. Nurme deodorants do not contain clay, which would make the deodorant crumbly, so you do not have to worry about unpleasant crumbling pieces. Also, the deodorant does not leave the underarms greasy, instead, it leaves them feeling is dry and secure.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eLavender essential oil is known for its antiseptic and anti-inflammatory properties and will make your armpits smell pleasant. Sage essential oil has antiperspirant properties.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ealuminum-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003edo not contain synthetic dyes or fragrances\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eparaben-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e“zero waste” – in addition to the deodorant itself, the packaging that is made out of cardboard, is also environmentally friendly\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eensures the natural functioning of the body\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e100% NATURAL and 100% CRUELTY-FREE\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRemove the cap and squeeze the bottom of the tube, so a few centimeters of the deodorant stick comes out. If the stick does not want to move in the tube, hold it in your hand and warm it a little, you can move the tube around in your hands. This will warm up the deodorant and unstick it from the sides of the tube, so it starts moving in the package. If the stick tends to sink back to the bottom, squeeze it back up and hold it in place with your fingers placed under the stick.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlways apply the deodorant to clean, washed, dry skin. Place the stick on warm skin for a few seconds to soften it and then rub it all over the armpit. Don’t forget that\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eless is more\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– a thicker layer doesn’t mean longer protection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAllow the deodorant to dry and absorb for a few minutes before dressing. Then you are ready to continue your day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Cera Alba (Beewax), Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Sodium Bicarbonate, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Lavandula Angustifolia  (Lavender) Oil, Salvia Sclarea (Clary Sage) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E), Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Citral*, Geraniol*,  Linalool*, Limonene*, *Occurs naturally in essential oils.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52398538490183,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-natural-deodorant-lavender-and-sage-80g-6030346.webp?v=1762389108"},{"product_id":"nurme-natural-deodorant-lemon-and-eucolyptus-80g","title":"NURME Natural Deodorant Lemon and Eucolyptus 80g","description":"\u003cdiv\u003eThe essential oils contained in deodorants have odor-neutralizing properties and, in addition, the baking soda in deodorants prevents the spread of odorous bacteria. Nurme deodorants do not contain clay, which would make the deodorant crumbly, so you do not have to worry about unpleasant crumbling pieces. Also, the deodorant does not leave the underarms greasy, instead, it leaves them feeling is dry and secure.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ealuminum-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003edo not contain synthetic dyes or fragrances\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eparaben-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e“zero waste” – in addition to the deodorant itself, the packaging that is made out of cardboard, is also environmentally friendly\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eensures the natural functioning of the body\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e100% NATURAL and 100% CRUELTY-FREE\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRemove the cap and squeeze the bottom of the tube, so a few centimeters of the deodorant stick comes out. If the stick does not want to move in the tube, hold it in your hand and warm it a little, you can move the tube around in your hands. This will warm up the deodorant and unstick it from the sides of the tube, so it starts moving in the package. If the stick tends to sink back to the bottom, squeeze it back up and hold it in place with your fingers placed under the stick.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlways apply the deodorant to clean, washed, dry skin. Place the stick on warm skin for a few seconds to soften it and then rub it all over the armpit. Don’t forget that\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eless is more\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– a thicker layer doesn’t mean longer protection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAllow the deodorant to dry and absorb for a few minutes before dressing. Then you are ready to continue your day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Cera Alba (Beewax), Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Sodium Bicarbonate, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Citrus Limon (Lemon) Peel Oil, Eucalyptus Globulus (Eucalyptus) Leaf Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E), Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Citral *, Linalool*, Limonene*, *Occurs naturally in essential oils.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52398560706887,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-natural-deodorant-lemon-and-eucolyptus-80g-5650515.webp?v=1762389110"},{"product_id":"nurme-natural-deodorant-ylang-ylang-and-bergamot-80g","title":"NURME Natural Deodorant Ylang-Ylang and Bergamot 80g","description":"\u003cdiv\u003eThe essential oils contained in deodorants have odor-neutralizing properties and, in addition, the baking soda in deodorants prevents the spread of odorous bacteria. Nurme deodorants do not contain clay, which would make the deodorant crumbly, so you do not have to worry about unpleasant crumbling pieces. Also, the deodorant does not leave the underarms greasy, instead, it leaves them feeling is dry and secure.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYlang-ylang and bergamot give the deodorant a sweet scent.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ealuminum-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003edo not contain synthetic dyes or fragrances\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eparaben-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e“zero waste” – in addition to the deodorant itself, the packaging that is made out of cardboard, is also environmentally friendly\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eensures the natural functioning of the body\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e100% NATURAL and 100% CRUELTY-FREE\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRemove the cap and squeeze the bottom of the tube, so a few centimeters of the deodorant stick comes out. If the stick does not want to move in the tube, hold it in your hand and warm it a little, you can move the tube around in your hands. This will warm up the deodorant and unstick it from the sides of the tube, so it starts moving in the package. If the stick tends to sink back to the bottom, squeeze it back up and hold it in place with your fingers placed under the stick.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlways apply the deodorant to clean, washed, dry skin. Place the stick on warm skin for a few seconds to soften it and then rub it all over the armpit. Don’t forget that\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eless is more\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– a thicker layer doesn’t mean longer protection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAllow the deodorant to dry and absorb for a few minutes before dressing. Then you are ready to continue your day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Cera Alba (Beewax), Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Sodium Bicarbonate, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Cananga Odorata (Ylang Ylang) Flower Oil, Citrus Aurantium Bergamia (Bergamot) Leaf Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E), Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Benzyl Alcohol*, Eugenol*, Isoeugenol*, Benzyl Salicylate*, Geraniol* Farnesol*, Linalool*, Benzyl Benzoate * Limonene*, *Occurs naturally in essential oils.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52398572142919,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-natural-deodorant-ylang-ylang-and-bergamot-80g-4201949.webp?v=1762389109"},{"product_id":"nurme-natural-deodorant-spearmint-and-rosemary-80g","title":"NURME Natural Deodorant Spearmint and Rosemary 80g","description":"\u003cdiv\u003eThe essential oils contained in deodorants have odor-neutralizing properties and, in addition, the baking soda in deodorants prevents the spread of odorous bacteria. Nurme deodorants do not contain clay, which would make the deodorant crumbly, so you do not have to worry about unpleasant crumbling pieces. Also, the deodorant does not leave the underarms greasy, instead, it leaves them feeling is dry and secure.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ealuminum-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003edo not contain synthetic dyes or fragrances\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eparaben-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e“zero waste” – in addition to the deodorant itself, the packaging that is made out of cardboard, is also environmentally friendly\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eensures the natural functioning of the body\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e100% NATURAL and 100% CRUELTY-FREE\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRemove the cap and squeeze the bottom of the tube, so a few centimeters of the deodorant stick comes out. If the stick does not want to move in the tube, hold it in your hand and warm it a little, you can move the tube around in your hands. This will warm up the deodorant and unstick it from the sides of the tube, so it starts moving in the package. If the stick tends to sink back to the bottom, squeeze it back up and hold it in place with your fingers placed under the stick.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlways apply the deodorant to clean, washed, dry skin. Place the stick on warm skin for a few seconds to soften it and then rub it all over the armpit. Don’t forget that\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eless is more\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– a thicker layer doesn’t mean longer protection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAllow the deodorant to dry and absorb for a few minutes before dressing. Then you are ready to continue your day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Cera Alba (Beewax), Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Sodium Bicarbonate, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Mentha viridis (Spearmint) Leaf Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E), Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Linalool*, Limonene*, *Occurs naturally in essential oils.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52398600388935,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-natural-deodorant-spearmint-and-rosemary-80g-9673786.webp?v=1762389110"},{"product_id":"nurme-natural-deodorant-lime-patchouli-80g","title":"NURME Natural Deodorant Lime Patchouli 80g","description":"\u003cdiv\u003eThe essential oils contained in deodorants have odor-neutralizing properties and, in addition, the baking soda in deodorants prevents the spread of odorous bacteria. Nurme deodorants do not contain clay, which would make the deodorant crumbly, so you do not have to worry about unpleasant crumbling pieces. Also, the deodorant does not leave the underarms greasy, instead, it leaves them feeling is dry and secure.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ealuminum-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003edo not contain synthetic dyes or fragrances\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eparaben-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e“zero waste” – in addition to the deodorant itself, the packaging that is made out of cardboard, is also environmentally friendly\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eensures the natural functioning of the body\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e100% NATURAL and 100% CRUELTY-FREE\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRemove the cap and squeeze the bottom of the tube, so a few centimeters of the deodorant stick comes out. If the stick does not want to move in the tube, hold it in your hand and warm it a little, you can move the tube around in your hands. This will warm up the deodorant and unstick it from the sides of the tube, so it starts moving in the package. If the stick tends to sink back to the bottom, squeeze it back up and hold it in place with your fingers placed under the stick.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlways apply the deodorant to clean, washed, dry skin. Place the stick on warm skin for a few seconds to soften it and then rub it all over the armpit. Don’t forget that\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eless is more\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– a thicker layer doesn’t mean longer protection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAllow the deodorant to dry and absorb for a few minutes before dressing. Then you are ready to continue your day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Cera Alba (Beewax), Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Sodium Bicarbonate, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Citrus Aurantifolia Oil, Pogostemon Cablin (Patchouli) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E), Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Citral*, Geraniol*,  Linalool*, Limonene*, *Occurs naturally in essential oils.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52398633517383,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-natural-deodorant-lime-patchouli-80g-6897932.webp?v=1762389109"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/deodorant.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}